# Muster configuration (OPTIONAL).
#
# The site runs fully without any of this — every var here has a sensible default,
# so a fork works with zero setup. Copy to `.env.local` for local dev, or set them
# in your host's env (e.g. Cloudflare Pages) for production.

# --- Site origin ---
# Used to resolve the canonical URL, the sitemap/robots host, and the OpenGraph /
# Twitter card image absolutely. Defaults to the production site; set this to your
# own domain when deploying a fork so those point at your copy, not muster.fusionspace.co.
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://muster.fusionspace.co
